611
00:28:13,230 --> 00:28:14,150
Your Majesty.

612
00:28:14,280 --> 00:28:15,980
I have something to report.

613
00:28:16,600 --> 00:28:17,490
Minister Jiang.

614
00:28:18,140 --> 00:28:19,080
