00:33:51,310 --> 00:33:52,200
Aunt, please investigate it.

767
00:33:52,280 --> 00:33:53,550
This has nothing to do with Shu.

768
00:33:53,790 --> 00:33:54,390
You...

769
00:33:54,960 --> 00:33:55,660
